website_summaries.verdict: Picky rabbits who sneakily eat around their healthy hay pellets will flip when you provide them with a bowl of these assorted, healthy, and colorful tidbits.

product_meta.title: Supremepetfoods Russel Rabbit Food
product_meta.description: Size:6 lbA tasty muesli-style mix which stimulates a rabbits appetite and foraging instincts, with a selection of ingredients ideally suited to keep it healthy and satisfied. Alfalfa is included for fibre, calcium and other vegetables are included to provide the necessary protein, vitamins and minerals. Its special formulation will keep rabbits fit, inside and out. Ingredients: [return]Alfalfa Pellets, Flaked Corn, Whole Oats, Alfalfa Stalk, Flaked Field Peas, Flaked Beans, Linseed Cake, Carrots, Natural Flavorings, Vitamins & Minerals.
feature_bullets: A nutritionally balanced, tasty mix for adult rabbits
Best ever taste - no added sugar
With tasty Timothy Hay - a fabulous source of fiber
Suitable for all breeds including dwarf rabbits
